{"tid":2230472,"cid":15,"subCid":0,"title":"發覺好多散戶都會用 hypothesis (假說) 黎炒股","createTime":"2020-10-05T02:53:16.000Z","updateTime":"2020-10-05T03:05:09.000Z","uid":123335,"like":6,"dislike":3,"uniUserReply":9,"replies":[{"pid":"98b1120a4955fba78f98be5179710dd46f7d62c7","tid":2230472,"uid":123335,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-10-05T02:53:16.000Z","msg":"稍為讀過少少初中science <br />\n都知成個流程係：<br />\n觀察&rarr;假說&rarr; 實驗&rarr;分析&rarr;結論 <br />\n<br />\n舉個例，<br />\n近排 d人（觀察）到trump 中肺炎 <br />\n心中就有個（假說）<br />\n心諗：股市實大跌啦，股災呀，熊佢老母西<br />\n<br />\n但如此（假說），<br />\n根本冇經過實驗去作分析, eg backtest <br />\n<br />\n貿貿然就由（假說）跳 step 去（結論）<br />\n用下腦都知唔 make sense<br />\n你地根本係賭緊錢 <br />\n所以咪成日輸錢囉 <img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"8d1dadadd483bc9bbbdd58fc7ca1114501e54838","tid":2230472,"uid":73241,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-10-05T02:53:31.000Z","msg":"所言甚是"},{"pid":"629a8975af0e286f2cb435b11e4d93450ae905ed","tid":2230472,"uid":162558,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-10-05T02:53:51.000Z","msg":"冇錯"},{"pid":"cb0ab2a658a8352c8190ee19e79abcb6537ab8d6","tid":2230472,"uid":281020,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-10-05T02:54:13.000Z","msg":"agger"},{"pid":"b0ab3460233f5713c651337b002024008d06ea43","tid":2230472,"uid":23198,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-10-05T02:55:48.000Z","msg":"thanks for sharing👌🏻"},{"pid":"e6c1794319b2ff2f480339d4514965da3f2f2cfe","tid":2230472,"uid":300630,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-10-05T02:56:58.000Z","msg":"Noted with thanks"},{"pid":"4e16ae98da20fca04edbb4ff529a96479db42d35","tid":2230472,"uid":214177,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-10-05T02:57:30.000Z","msg":"講經咩 <br />\n一句講哂 好多散戶買股票都係估估下"},{"pid":"d7286b1a425014d1f9f67b292fddf8eb0b980c3f","tid":2230472,"uid":225437,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-10-05